/PelEntryUndefined.php

Description
Description | Classes | Includes

Classes used to hold data for Exif tags of format undefined.

This file contains the base class PelEntryUndefined and the subclasses PelEntryUserComment which should be used to manage the PelTag::USER_COMMENT tag, and PelEntryVersion which is used to manage entries with version information.
